%%wiki

Cream Finery Theme
==================

The Cream Finery Theme is a Metacity- and GTK+ Theme based on Ubuntu's new Radiance theme, but with a lot of improvements and enhancements.

Current state
-------------
Pictures are worth a thousand words:

.. image:: http://ubuntu-pics.de/thumb/61453/finery_1_JDmjwA.png
.. image:: http://ubuntu-pics.de/thumb/61455/twf_ix8uB8.png

Ideas
-----
* Less gloss on buttons
* More emboss on progressbar background
* Simple, flat list items
* Top margin of Notebook-Tabs should be more than 0px
* Menubar color == window background color, while toolbar's getting a gradient
* Fix the weird shade switching (light/dark, dark/light) when hovering over a ComboBox
